  - Body: My Shaykli used lo say thal both qabd and bast are the result
      of one spiritual influence, which descends from God on Man.
    By: Hujwiri
    Source:
      Title: Kashf
      Page: 375
---
The contraction (qabd) of hearts consists in the expansion (bast) of
souls, and the expansion of hearts in the contraction of souls.
